OL,3,CHow Starmer may have seen off a coup
OL,5,FRebel MPs who want Sir Keir Starmer
OL,6,Fremoved are feeling tactically
OL,7,Foutmaneuvered.
OL,9,FIf they are minded to launch a coup
OL,10,Fafter potential Labour humiliation in
OL,11,Fthe May 7 elections, their ability to
OL,12,Forganise will be hugely constrained -
OL,13,Fbecause the Commons will not be
OL,14,Fsitting until the King reopens
OL,15,Fparliament on May 13 and announces the
OL,16,Fprime minister's new legislative
OL,17,Fprogramme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
